00:14:56.586 --> 00:15:01.796
Of course, there is nothing wrong with asking questions per se - questions are

00:15:01.806 --> 00:15:07.812
healthy and if there are no answers then it is completely justified to be sceptical.

00:15:08.636 --> 00:15:14.606
The problem is that the Loose Change films are very easily debunked, but if

00:15:14.616 --> 00:15:20.486
you watch them then it’s so easy to get caught up in the conspiracy theory that

00:15:20.516 --> 00:15:24.446
even when you’re presented with the evidence, you don’t want to believe it.

00:15:25.486 --> 00:15:31.936
And, although the films are now a little dated, they seem a little old, and there are

00:15:31.936 --> 00:15:38.066
